Fed Begins Purchases of Treasury Inflation Protected Securities

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-09-27T14:15:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/fed-begins-purchases-of-treasury-inflation-protected-securities.html
The  Federal Reserve  began buying Treasury 
Inflation Protected Securities as part of an asset-purchase program aimed at 
lowering borrowing costs and stimulating economic growth.  The Federal Reserve Bank of  New York  listed the securities it is 
considering for purchase during today's operation on its website.
 http://www.newyorkfed.org/markets/pomo/display/index.cfm  